# cargo-fuzz build output and crash artifacts are transient.
/target
/artifacts
/coverage

# The seed corpus IS committed (fleet property-and-fuzz spec). cargo-fuzz mutates
# copies in-place during a run and drops newly-discovered inputs here; keep the
# checked-in seeds but do not commit the fuzzer's own generated growth.
# (Explicit: corpus/ is tracked; nothing here ignores it.)
